{"markdownMeta":{"data":{"title":"解决 Tailwindcss 和 emmet 之间的提示冲突","description":"解决 Tailwindcss 和 emmet 之间的提示冲突","slug":"/tailwindcss","date":"2023-11-25T00:00:00.000Z","author":"Lycoiref","tags":["Tailwindcss","Emmet","VSCode"]},"content":"\n# 解决 Tailwindcss 和 emmet 之间的提示冲突\n\n安装 tailwindcss 插件后，突然惊奇的发现 emmet 快捷指令失效了，\n这令笔者非常不爽，一番排查下来原来是 file.associations 导致\nemmet 不认 css 和 scss 文件了，自然也就无法触发提示，解决方法如下：\n\n```json:settings.json\n// tailwindcss\n  \"files.associations\": {\n    \"*.css\": \"tailwindcss\",\n    \"*.scss\": \"tailwindcss\",\n  },\n  \"editor.quickSuggestions\": {\n    \"strings\": \"on\"\n  },\n  \"tailwindCSS.emmetCompletions\": true,\n  \"emmet.includeLanguages\": {\n    \"tailwindcss\": \"css\"\n  },\n```\n"}}